# endTime

**Instance Property**

The presentation time of the first frame following the end of a reaction effect.

## Declaration

```swift
var endTime: CMTime { get }
```

## Discussion

The value is [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/CoreMedia/CMTime/invalid] while the effect is in progress, but changes to a valid time when the reaction effect completes and the system removes it from the list of [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVCaptureDevice/reactionEffectsInProgress].

## Configuring the effect state

- **reactionType**: The type of reaction.
- **AVCaptureReactionType**: Constants that indicate the type of reaction that an effect can perform.
- **startTime**: The presentation time of the first frame where the system renders the effect.
